---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import GithubIcon from "../components/GithubIcon.astro";
import RightArrow from "../components/RightArrow.astro";
import LinkIcon from "../components/LinkIcon.astro";
import "@/styles/globals.css";
import {
  Card,
  CardContent,
  CardDescription,
  CardFooter,
  CardHeader,
  CardTitle,
} from "@/components/ui/card";
import { Button } from "@/components/ui/button";
---

<Layout>
  <main class="bg-slate-50">
    <div class="px-5 md:px-0 md:mx-auto md:max-w-3xl">
      <div class="">
        <div class="pt-20 flex items-center justify-between">
          <h2 class="text-indigo-700 text-2xl md:text-4xl font-extralight">
            Farooq A. Khan
          </h2>
          <div class="flex items-center space-x-2">
            <a target="_blank" href="https://github.com/Farooq-azam-khan">
              <GithubIcon />
            </a>
            <a
              target="_blank"
              href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/farooq-khan-46167bb5/"
            >
              <img
                alt="linkedin logo"
                class="w-8 h-8"
                src="/linkedin-logo-512.webp"
              />
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <h1 class="text-gray-800 text-5xl md:text-7xl font-bold">
          Machine Learning Engineer
        </h1>
        <p
          class="mt-14 md:mt-32 text-md md:text-xl italic leading-loose tracking-wider lg:max-w-3xl"
        >
          <div>
            Machine Learning Engineer specializing in delivering scalable AI
            solutions.
          </div>
          <div>
            <span>Artificial Intelligence</span>: Working on the use of graph
            algorithms and reinforcement learning algorithms to develop enhanced
            large language models.
          </div>
          <div>
            <span>Model Deployment Specialist</span>: Delivering scalable
            solutions with VLLMs, Ollama, and NVIDIA TensorRT for optimized
            model serving pipelines.
          </div>
          <div>
            <span>Cutting-Edge Research & Application</span>: Bridging theory
            and practice to create impactful, intelligent systems.
          </div>
        </p>
        <div class="mt-32 md:mt-64 rounded-md">
          <h2
            class="text-indigo-800 text-xl font-semibold tracking-wide uppercase"
          >
            Blog Highlights
          </h2>
          <div class="space-y-5">
            <Card>
              <CardHeader>
                <CardTitle
                  >Scaling LLMs with Triton Inference Server: A Hands-on Guide</CardTitle
                >
                <CardDescription
                  >Get hands-on experience with deploying Large Language Models
                  (LLMs) at scale using NVIDIA's Triton Inference Server.
                </CardDescription>
              </CardHeader>
              <CardContent />
              <CardFooter
                ><a
                  href="https://blog.farooqkhan.ca/fast-llm-inferencing"
                  target="blank_"
                  class="inline-flex items-center px-3 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-center text-white bg-indigo-700 rounded-lg hover:bg-indigo-800 focus:ring-4 focus:outline-none focus:ring-blue-300 dark:bg-indigo-600 dark:hover:bg-indigo-700 dark:focus:ring-indgio-800"
                  >Read more<RightArrow /></a
                ></CardFooter
              >
            </Card>
            <Card>
              <CardHeader>
                <CardTitle>
                  Term Frequency-Inverse Document Frequency
                </CardTitle>
                <CardDescription
                  >In this tutorial we will look at what TF and IDF are and how
                  they can be use to process text data for Machine learning.
                </CardDescription>
              </CardHeader>
              <CardContent />
              <CardFooter
                ><a
                  href="https://blog.farooqkhan.ca/tfidf"
                  target="blank_"
                  class="inline-flex items-center px-3 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-center text-white bg-indigo-700 rounded-lg hover:bg-indigo-800 focus:ring-4 focus:outline-none focus:ring-blue-300 dark:bg-indigo-600 dark:hover:bg-indigo-700 dark:focus:ring-indgio-800"
                  >Read more<RightArrow /></a
                ></CardFooter
              >
            </Card>
            <Card>
              <CardHeader>
                <CardTitle>Large Scale Vector Comparison</CardTitle>
                <CardDescription>
                  In this post, we will look at the quora qna dataset and aim to
                  encode and compare all question pairs. The purpose of is to
                  look at a real dataset.</CardDescription
                >
              </CardHeader>
              <CardContent />
              <CardFooter
                ><a
                  href="https://blog.farooqkhan.ca/cosine-similarity-pt-2"
                  target="blank_"
                  class="inline-flex items-center px-3 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-center text-white bg-indigo-700 rounded-lg hover:bg-indigo-800 focus:ring-4 focus:outline-none focus:ring-blue-300 dark:bg-indigo-600 dark:hover:bg-indigo-700 dark:focus:ring-indgio-800"
                  >Read more
                  <RightArrow />
                </a></CardFooter
              >
            </Card>
            <Card>
              <CardHeader>
                <CardTitle>
                  Comparing Vectors with Cosine Simlarity Function
                </CardTitle>
                <CardDescription>
                  This tutorial will focus on the math behind text vector
                  similarity using numpy, pytorch, and stentence-transformers
                  libraries in python.</CardDescription
                >
              </CardHeader>
              <CardContent />
              <CardFooter
                ><a
                  href="https://blog.farooqkhan.ca/cosine-similarity"
                  target="blank_"
                  class="inline-flex items-center px-3 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-center text-white bg-indigo-700 rounded-lg hover:bg-indigo-800 focus:ring-4 focus:outline-none focus:ring-blue-300 dark:bg-indigo-600 dark:hover:bg-indigo-700 dark:focus:ring-indgio-800"
                  >Read more<RightArrow /></a
                ></CardFooter
              >
            </Card>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <section class="mt-32">
      <div class="px-5 space-y-14 md:px-0 md:mx-auto md:max-w-3xl">
        <h2
          class="text-indigo-500 text-lg font-semibold tracking-wide uppercase"
        >
          Personal AI Projects
        </h2>
        <div class="grid gap-y-10 md:gap-x-10 md:grid-cols-2">
          <Card>
            <CardHeader>
              <CardTitle>Race Car RL Agent</CardTitle>
              <CardDescription>Comming Soon...</CardDescription>
            </CardHeader>
            <CardContent />
          </Card>
          <Card>
            <CardHeader>
              <CardTitle>Garbage Classification with CNN </CardTitle>
              <CardDescription>
                Efficient Net finetuned on Classifying different types of
                Garbage.
              </CardDescription>
            </CardHeader>
            <CardContent />
            <CardFooter>
              <a
                href="https://github.com/Farooq-azam-khan/cps803-course-project"
                target="blank_"
                class="rounded-lg"><GithubIcon /></a
              ></CardFooter
            >
          </Card>
          <Card>
            <CardHeader>
              <CardTitle> Haiku Generator</CardTitle>
              <CardDescription
                >Prompt engineering experimentation to generate Haikus with
                LLMs.</CardDescription
              >
            </CardHeader>
            <CardContent />
            <CardFooter
              ><a
                href="https://github.com/Farooq-azam-khan/haiku/"
                target="blank_"
                class="rounded-lg"><GithubIcon /></a
              ></CardFooter
            >
          </Card>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mt-32">
      <div class="px-5 space-y-14 md:px-0 md:mx-auto md:max-w-3xl">
        <h2
          class="text-indigo-500 text-lg font-semibold tracking-wide uppercase"
        >
          Additional Projects
        </h2>
        <ol class="grid gap-y-10 md:gap-x-10 md:grid-cols-2 mt-14">
          <Card>
            <CardHeader>
              <CardTitle> D3Js Reference Tutorial </CardTitle>
              <CardDescription>
                Web app to reference D3 library and its many features.</CardDescription
              >
            </CardHeader>
            <CardContent />
            <CardFooter className="space-x-3">
              <a
                target="blank_"
                href="https://farooq-azam-khan.github.io/d3js-tutorials/"
                ><LinkIcon /></a
              >
              <a
                href="https://github.com/Farooq-azam-khan/d3js-tutorials"
                target="blank_"><GithubIcon /></a
              ></CardFooter
            >
          </Card>

          <Card>
            <CardHeader>
              <CardTitle>Chat App</CardTitle>
              <CardDescription>
                A Chat application built to explore web socket connections and
                server client relations with the protocol. App built with elm,
                expressjs, and websockets.
              </CardDescription>
            </CardHeader>
            <CardContent />
            <CardFooter
              ><a
                href="https://github.com/Farooq-azam-khan/chat-app-elm"
                target="blank_"
                class="rounded-lg"><GithubIcon /></a
              ></CardFooter
            >
          </Card>
          <Card>
            <CardHeader>
              <CardTitle> Twitch Python Discord Bot </CardTitle>
              <CardDescription>Discord bot built with Python.</CardDescription>
            </CardHeader>
            <CardContent />
            <CardFooter
              ><a
                href="https://github.com/Farooq-azam-khan/twitch-api-discord-bot"
                target="blank_"
                class="rounded-lg"><GithubIcon /></a
              ></CardFooter
            >
          </Card>
          <Card>
            <CardHeader>
              <CardTitle> Rust Tauri App </CardTitle>
              <CardDescription>
                Experimental app designed to test the features offered by Tauri
                library.</CardDescription
              >
            </CardHeader>
            <CardContent />
            <CardFooter
              ><a
                href="https://github.com/Farooq-azam-khan/color-picker-tauri-test-project"
                target="blank_"
                class="rounded-lg"><GithubIcon /></a
              ></CardFooter
            >
          </Card>
        </ol>
      </div>
    </section>
    <section class="mt-32">
      <div class="px-5 md:px-0 md:mx-auto md:max-w-3xl">
        <h2
          class="text-indigo-500 text-lg font-semibold tracking-wide uppercase"
        >
          Additional Interests
        </h2>
        <ul>
          <div>
            <h3 class="mb-2 text-xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900">
              Artificial Intelligence
            </h3>
            <p class="mb-3 text-lg font-normal text-gray-700">
              Machine Learning, Reinforcement Learning, NLP, MLOps.
            </p>
          </div><div>
            <h3 class="mb-2 text-xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900">
              Software Engineering
            </h3>
            <p class="mb-3 text-lg font-normal text-gray-700">
              Prompt Egineering, Backend Development, Rust, Python, Graph
              Database, Scalable Model Deployment.
            </p>
          </div><div>
            <h3 class="mb-2 text-xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900">
              Functional Programming
            </h3>
            <p class="mb-3 text-lg font-normal text-gray-700">
              Category Thoery, Elm Programming, Haskell.
            </p>
          </div><div>
            <h3 class="mb-2 text-xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900">
              Mathematics
            </h3><p class="mb-3 text-lg font-normal text-gray-700">
              Fourier Analysis, Linear Albegra, Statistics, Graph Thoery.
            </p>
          </div>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>
